SQL_STMT_U.val: select s.kd_kalender_dag positionDate, s.valueDate from ( select kd.*, wd.*, rank() over (partition by kd.kd_kalender_dag order by wd.valueDate) as days from kalender_dagen kd, ( select d.kd_kalender_dag valueDate from kalender_dagen d left outer join kalender_per_beurs k on k.nwb_niet_werkdag = d.kd_kalender_dag and k.nwb_beursnummer = ~1 where d.kd_kalender_dag between ~2 and ~5 and k.nwb_niet_werkdag is null order by d.kd_kalender_dag) wd where kd.kd_kalender_dag between ~2 and ~3 and wd.valueDate>= kd.kd_kalender_dag order by kd.kd_kalender_dag, wd.valueDate) s where days = ~4
